text: Osokorivka () is an inhabited locality in Ukraine and it may refer to: * Osokorivka, Bobrovytsia Raion, a village in Bobrovytsia Raion, Chernihiv Oblast * Osokorivka, Synelnykove Raion, a village in Synelnykove Raion, Dnipropetrovsk Oblast * Osokorivka, Novovorontsovka Raion, a village in Novovorontsovka Raion, Kherson Oblast
title: Osokorivka
